    REPLACE_TEXTUALLY CASE_INSENSITIVE ~%tutu_scripth%obelite%~ ~dw#mihoe~
    REPLACE_TEXTUALLY CASE_INSENSITIVE ~%tutu_scripth%obgoa_a%~ ~dw#mihoa~
    REPLACE_TEXTUALLY CASE_INSENSITIVE ~%tutu_scripth%obgoa_b%~ ~dw#mihob~

